🎬 WebM to MP4 Converter (Windows Batch Script)

A simple drag-and-drop batch script that converts `.webm` files to `.mp4` using FFmpeg.

🚀 Features
- Drag and drop conversion
- Supports multiple files
- Uses H.264 + AAC for compatibility
- No GUI required

🛠 Requirements
- Windows OS
- FFmpeg installed
- Update the FFmpeg path inside the script if necessary

📦 How to Use
1. Download the script.
2. Install FFmpeg.
3. Drag one or more `.webm` files onto `ConvertToMP4.bat`.
4. Your `.mp4` files will be created in the same folder.

